<h2>Curator 技能策展系统</h2>

<h3>生命周期状态机</h3>

<pre class="mermaid">graph LR
    A[active] -->|stale_after_days (30天)| B[stale]
    B -->|archive_after_days (90天)| C[archived]
    A -->|pinned| A
    C -.->|restore| A
    B -.->|restore| A</pre>

<h3>自动转换（纯函数，无 LLM）</h3>

<pre><code class="language-python">def apply_automatic_transitions(skills, config):
    \"\"\"基于最后活动时间戳自动标记\"\"\"
    for skill in skills:
        if skill.is_pinned:
            continue
        latest = latest_activity_at(skill)  # 从 .usage.json
        if age > archive_after_days:
            skill.state = 'archived'
        elif age > stale_after_days:
            skill.state = 'stale'</code></pre>

